---
// src/components/AboutUs.astro
---
<section id="nosotros" class="about">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-badge">Quiénes Somos</div>
    <h2>Transformamos la forma en que <span>conectás con tus clientes</span></h2>
    <p class="about-subtitle">
      Somos un equipo apasionado por la tecnología y las ventas. Creemos que cada conversación es una oportunidad, y nuestra misión es que no pierdas ninguna.
    </p>

    <div class="about-grid">
      <!-- Card 1: Misión -->
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nuestra Misión</h3>
        <p>Democratizar la automatización inteligente para que emprendedores y pymes puedan competir con las grandes marcas, cerrando más ventas sin perder el toque humano.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Visión -->
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon vision">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28">
            <path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nuestra Visión</h3>
        <p>Ser la plataforma líder en Latinoamérica en gestión inteligente de conversaciones, ayudando a miles de negocios a escalar sus ventas con inteligencia artificial.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Valores -->
      <div class="about-card">
        <div class="card-icon values">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" width="28" height="28">
            <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Nuestros Valores</h3>
        <p>Innovación constante, transparencia radical y compromiso con el éxito de nuestros clientes. Cada feature que construimos nace de una necesidad real.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 7rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8f9ff 100%);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px;
    right: -120px;
    width: 400px;
    height: 400px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -80px;
    left: -80px;
    width: 300px;
    height: 300px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    width: 90%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.08), rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.15));
    color: var(--color-primary-blue);
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.12);
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  h2 span {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-blue), #6366f1);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .about-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto 4rem;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .about-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
    text-align: left;
    transition: all 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .about-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary-blue), var(--color-primary-green));
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 0.35s;
  }

  .about-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.15);
  }

  .about-card:hover::before {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.08), rgba(58, 61, 238, 0.15));
    color: var(--color-primary-blue);
    transition: all 0.35s;
  }

  .card-icon.vision {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08), rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15));
    color: #6366f1;
  }

  .card-icon.values {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.08), rgba(21, 198, 59, 0.15));
    color: var(--color-primary-green);
  }

  .about-card:hover .card-icon {
    transform: scale(1.1);
  }

  .about-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .about-card p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Stats */
  .about-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3rem;
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.35rem;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary-blue), #6366f1);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-medium);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .stat-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 50px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, #e2e8f0, transparent);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-left: auto;
      margin-right: auto;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .about-stats {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .stat-divider {
      width: 60px;
      height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #e2e8f0, transparent);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }

    .about-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
